### ============================================================
### PROMOCODES — Apply Promo Code, List Active Codes
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000
### Both endpoints are PUBLIC (no auth required)
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# APPLY PROMOCODE
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Apply Promocode — valid code with sufficient order total
POST {{baseUrl}}/promocodes/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "SAVE10",
  "order_total": 5000
}

###

### [SUCCESS] Apply Promocode — another valid code
POST {{baseUrl}}/promocodes/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "WELCOME20",
  "order_total": 10000
}

###

### [FAIL — Not Found] Apply Promocode — invalid/expired code (404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/promocodes/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "FAKECODE999",
  "order_total": 5000
}

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Apply Promocode — order total below minimum (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/promocodes/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "SAVE10",
  "order_total": 100
}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Apply Promocode — SQL injection in code field (404/400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/promocodes/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "' OR '1'='1",
  "order_total": 5000
}

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Apply Promocode — negative order total (422/400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/promocodes/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "SAVE10",
  "order_total": -100
}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# LIST ACTIVE PROMOCODES
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] List Active Promocodes — default pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/promocodes/active/list

###

### [SUCCESS] List Active Promocodes — custom pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/promocodes/active/list?skip=0&limit=5

###

### [FAIL — Validation] List Active Promocodes — limit exceeds max (422)
GET {{baseUrl}}/promocodes/active/list?limit=9999

###

### [FAIL — Validation] List Active Promocodes — negative skip (422)
GET {{baseUrl}}/promocodes/active/list?skip=-1
